title: Develop Self-Control To Rise Higher With God
itunes:title: Develop Self-Control To Rise Higher With God
description:
I get excited whenever I think of all the potential God has put inside each of us. We all have the capacity to grow and produce more than we’re producing right now. We all can do more for God. We have so much more inside us!Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit http://JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
